    "capitalDecisionRequires": ["profitable demand", "qualified staffing plan", "floor and utility readiness", "tooling and inspection budget", "working-capital reserve", "commissioning plan"],
    "deathSpiralProtection": "A missed payment or bad job creates a mentored recovery plan, renegotiation, staged investment, or lower-risk work. It never silently compounds into an unrecoverable save."
  },
